FBIS3-57425 "drsov017_b_94015" FBIS-SOV-94-017 Document Type:Daily Report 26 Jan 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Shaposhnikov Appointed Representative to Company LD2601113094 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1031 GMT 26 Jan 94 LD2601113094 Moscow ITAR-TASS Language: English Article Type:BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent] [Text] Moscow January 26 TASS -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin today signed a decree appointing Yevgeniy Shaposhnikov as presidential representative in the "Rosvooruzhenie" state company for exporting and importing weapons and military hardware, the presidential press service reported today.
